ice/plum-blossom-needle-therapy</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:16:20.000Z","msg":"咁你整完之後康復成點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無話要幾耐/做幾多次先完全散曬D瘀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我失頭哥好似都做過 之前踩單車炒車瘀到成個失頭都係<br />\n但我唔知佢用D針係唔係梅花針啦 但個時我見拔罐出黎D血都鮮紅 我抽左一次 目測個位無曬瘀之後無再去了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但有時飲酒 之前瘀個位都會發熱/少少痛 但我都無再處理了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826770d5cb714f13e18697c914a4e49000e7daff","tid":2111890,"uid":149973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"喜療妥"},{"pid":"335bb78161fa41e20a86a4c7d0ffde44ca401047","tid":2111890,"uid":33970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:42:18.000Z","msg":"佢係唔係凝血功能問題，皮下出血呀？驗下好喎"},{"pid":"c7c9f1697fb703a47c2b4416cde718dda375c1d3","tid":2111890,"uid":134620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3473175cf661edc143c35ef4aaa31df7d96e5e49","tid":2111890,"uid":51142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29a8f4cfc3690ebc3d93eefc372f4537df948c2b","tid":2111890,"uid":134774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:41:25.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦 可能係某d病引起"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T02:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係撞傷黎.唔係有病突然身體出現瘀青.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:44:28.000Z","msg":"人地係講緊某D病導致唔散瘀血啊,白血病,紫斑,免疫力疾病都會<br />\n長期唔散仲有機會導致脂肪瘤啊乜乜77瘤戈D<br />\n係擔生就帶佢睇醫生啦,連登問係咪想累死你老母?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}